{
  "description": "A wide-angle shot captures a serene coastal landscape at dusk or dawn. The focal point is a long, suspension bridge stretching across a vast body of water. The bridge is a pale grey against a vibrant sky transitioning from a warm orange near the horizon to cooler blues and greys higher up. Dark, layered clouds hang low, creating a dramatic and somewhat moody atmosphere. In the foreground, there's a narrow, concrete pier or pathway extending into the water from a small landmass with trees.  A ship is visible under the bridge. Distant hills or mountains are faintly visible through the haze and clouds. The water appears calm, reflecting the colors of the sky.",
